<P>
"WE'VE MADE MISTAKES, THERE'S NO QUESTION ABOUT THAT, BUT FEMA'S
<P>
SUPPOSED TO PROVIDE PEOPLE WITH RELIEF FROM EMERGENCIES AND 
<P>
DISASTERS, AND WE CERTAINLY HAD ONE HERE IN 1989, AND WE'RE OUT
<P>
THE 16-MILLION BUCKS, AND WE'RE LOOKING FOR A LITTLE MORE COOPERATION THAN WE'VE GOTTEN."
